options.content:
Multi-channel Fraud Detection 1

Objectives:

Deteksi transaksi transfer semua channel (ATM, MobileApp, IBank) dari beberapa account ke dalam satu account (BSI / Non BSI) yang sama dengan total nominal minimal 100jt rupiah dalam kurun waktu 1 jam

targets.rawSql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Sender)) AS Total_Account_Sender FROM uc04_data.results
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Receiver)) AS Total_Account_Receiver FROM uc04_data.results
SELECT COUNT(ATM_Trx_ID), COUNT(IBank_Trx_ID), COUNT(Mobile_Trx_ID) FROM uc04_data.results LIMIT 50
SELECT SUM(ATM_Trx_Amount), SUM(Mobile_Trx_Amount), SUM(IBank_Trx_Amount) FROM uc04_data.results LIMIT 50

AND (ATM_Trx_ID IN ($Filter_TransactionID) OR Mobile_Trx_ID IN ($Filter_TransactionID) OR IBank_Trx_ID IN ($Filter_TransactionID))
